title: VULAIRE CARPENTER PANTS OFFWHITE
body_html:
Vulaire’s carpenter pants is Designed with precision and crafted from premium fabric, these carpenter pants offer exceptional comfort and durability, The fabric is carefully selected to provide flexibility and resilience. ensuring the pants hold up under tough conditions while maintaining their sleek, structured look.

 

The standout detail is the signature “V” metal pins, placed throughout the design, adding a bold and unique touch that sets these pants apart. With functional pockets and reinforced stitching, these pants provide practicality, making them a versatile addition to any wardrobe.

 

Ideal for those who value both functionality and fashion, our carpenter pants are not just a statement piece, they’re built to last.

 

Model is 175cm height 70kg weight wearing size Medium 

 

 

PRODUCT CODE : VUL16177183

title: WHITE VULAIRE’S FLARED SWEATPANTS
body_html:
Vulaire's flared sweatpants crafted from premium 380 gsm French terry fleece, offering a comfortable, relaxed fit for both men and women. Designed with a modern streetwear aesthetic, the sweatpants feature a slight flare at the hem for an elevated, luxurious touch. The design is completed with Vulaire’s signature logo print, giving a refined streetwear appeal.

 

Composition: French terry fleece (380 gsm )
